This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment. To be able to give love, I must first discard the (unconscious) conviction "I am not worth being loved" and begin to love myself. Only then can my love be visible in the outside.Physical effect:Radiaesthetic reviews showed that rose quartz positively affects relatively many frequencies. description: ✨🌌 "You - you alone will have the stars as no one else has them...In one of the stars I shall be living. In one of them I shall be laughing. And so it will be as if all the stars were laughing, when you look at the sky at night..." 🌌✨Antoine de Saint-ExupéryEvery single one of my journals has a deeper meaning, it's just that customers unintentionally forget to read the descriptions and stand in awe in front of the physical item. It's understandable.  So I removed them, except this one.  The story about Petite Prince is profound and speaks about life, friendship, loss, love and all the inbetweens. So whenever you reach a different stage in your life, and your mental processes change - the understanding of the books you read changes with them.Yet, there's nothing like the calming feeling of an upcoming epiphany in The Little Prince's story, when the author and the reader discover what are those "things" that really matter in life... What matters in life to you? =) Ps. The Little Prince is what brought me and my husband closer together. name: Kind taucht nach Muschel, Anhänger, 925 Sterling Silber, Gießharz, Unikat, ECHTE Handarbeit
description: Kind taucht nach Muschel, Anhänger, Gießharz, 925 Sterling SilberDie kleinen Mini Muscheln sind echt und ich habe sie selber aus dem Rhein (Fluss) gesammelt.Im Harz sind Glitzerpartikel, die" Algen" sind aus echtem Moos.( Da die Farbe nur bedingt lichtecht ist habe ich den Preis von ursprünglich 115,-Euro auf 75,- Euro gesenkt. Das heißt der Käufer erklärt sich damit einverstanden das das Blau mit der Zeit blasser werden kann!!)Alles von Hand hergestellt! Fassung wie der Stein aus Harz. Dieser wurde in mehreren Schichten hergestellt.Von der Herstellung der Fassung konnte ich aus Platzgründen keine Bilder einstellen. Auch diese ist ein Unikat.Der Anhänger ist bis auf das Figürchen einmalig. Die Figur stammt aus dem Modellbau und ist 1:1 realistisch! (und nicht ganz billig) Dadurch das sie so klein ist und in Harz gegossen erkennt man nicht jedes Detail.Achtung: Farbabweichngen sind durch Kamera und Computerbildschirme gegeben. Je nach Hintergrund kommt der Anhänger durch seine Tranzparenz anders zur Geltung!!! Und der Anhänger leuchtet so natürlich nur in der Sonne. Im Hier war der Guß sehr aufwendig! Es ist auch schwierig und kostet Nerven, aber so spart man sich die Achterbahn fahrt...Inklusive Fassung Material und Zeitaufwand ist der Anhänger sehr, sehr Preisgünstig!!!Der Anhänger kommt mit Kette in Schmuckschachtel mit Zertifikat und ist ein Unikat.Die Herstellung ist aufwendig und kann sich über 3-4 Wochen ziehen!Zuerst denke ich mir etwas aus und ordne es in der Gießform an, das Harz wird natürlich jedes mal angerührt. Die Hälfte wird aufgegossen und nochmal mit Pinzette alles ordentlich platziert,Nach 24 Stunden wird  VORSICHTIG die zweite Schicht aufgegossen bis zur Oberflächenspannung.Dann muss das Harz mindestens eine Woche aushärten.Die Fassung ist von mir von Hand gemacht in dem ich starken Draht in Form gewalzt habe- ebenfalls zeitaufwendig mit zwischen glühen. Dann habe ich den Rand angeschmolzen und die Fassung rund gebogen angepasst und verlötet.  Öse angelötet und die Schlaufe ist ebenfalls Handarbeit.Der Harzanhänger wird angepasst und in die Fassung gedrückt. Diese ist breiter damit ich den Rest aufüllen kann mit noch einer Schicht Harz damit er fest sitzt.Dies ist eine KURZE Zusammenfassung,  es sind weitaus mehr Arbeitsschrichte!!!!! +-+Die Kettenlänge ist bis 50 cm Gratis- schöne stabile 925 Silberkette!Der Anhänger hat ziemlich genau die Größe eines 2 Euro Stückes, ) 2,5 cm.Je nachdem sieht dieser Anhänger besser an einer längeren Kette aus.AB 50 cm mich bitte VOR dem Kauf kontaktieren da ich ab dieser länge einen Aufpreis berechnen muss.In das Harz habe ich einen speziell dafür gemachten UV Schutz gemischt, dieser schützt das Harz vorm vergilben. Der Anhänger kann aber mit einer dafür geeigneten Paste wieder aufpoliert werden.Bei Fragen kann man mich gerne kontaktieren!Gemacht mit Herz <3Versand erfolgt als versichertes Einschreiben Weltweit!(Keine Packstation, und bitte nicht direkt vor dem Urlaub bestellen.)Hinweis: Die Farbe des Wassers ist nur bedingt Lichtecht!!

name: Sun Sign, (Divine/God Sign) Pendant, 585 Gold/ 925 Sterling Silver, with Chain, REAL Handmade
description: Sun pendant, 925 sterling silver, with 585 gold(Made to order!)I thought for such a trailer is slow time and a nice alternative to other characters....I had hoped it would be a little easier to implement, but it has become quite cumbersome.Since it is handmade, the trailer is not industrially perfect round.Here is some more information about this sign:Sun sign is the symbol of the divine and soul power. From the center, the divine power radiates to the outside.The symbol stands for the sun, Sunday and gold. It is also considered a powerful reinforcement sign, so that positive energies are amplified in all directions.Since the circle has neither beginning nor end, it also stands for infinity.The sun sign reflects the law of reflection and self-knowledge.Trust in yourself and the Divine independent of the outside.Recognition of one's own light and this from the inside (golden circle/point) to radiate /light outwards.It stands for God, the cosmic consciousness and enlightenment.Astrology= for the SunSun sign stands for the number 1Manufacturing process in brief:-Silver plate sawn out, polished and drilled in center hole-pre-polished and eyelet adapted and firmly soldered, polished-with cutter elaborately milled beams, then still with Diamantier file after machined- Self-made 585 gold wire guided through hole-from both sides gold wire with hammer pinned/ flat hammeredMeans the gold is not soldered on the surface,but passes through the silver plate, is forged, i.e. that in this case there is also more gold in the trailer than seen from the front!!!!Small trailer but a lot of work.The pendant comes in jewelry box with certificate!The chain length is included up to 50 cm.Please contact me BEFORE THE BUY if a longer chain is desired, as I have to charge a small extra charge from this length.Shipping takes place as INSURED EInletter worldwide!!!Made with heart! If you have any questions or wishes, please feel free to contact me. :)Dimensions:approx. 1.4 cm

description: Rose Quartz Gemstone and Healing Stone BraceletSymbolic effect:The delicate pink ish-red colour symbolizes the still young rose bud, which is just about to unfold. For this reason, rose quartz can be recommended for all life situations in which a change or new beginning takes place:Rose Quartz Raw StoneRose Quartz Raw Stonee.g. at birth, puberty, pregnancy, career change, menopause, divorce, euthanasia. With "gentle determination" the rose quartz helps to unfold itself and to realize its true needs.He stands for unconditional love, which is without judging. This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment. To be able to give love, I must first discard the (unconscious) conviction "I am not worth being loved" and begin to love myself. Only then can my love be visible in the outside.Physical effect:Radiaesthetic reviews showed that rose quartz positively affects relatively many frequencies. In particular, its effect in the area of the nervous system and in problems with the heart and blood circulation could be confirmed, probably due to the manganese content. description: Dieses Produkt basiert auf Spenden, bitte lies die Shopbeschreibung. ☀This is a donations-based item, please read shop description. ☀If you can play it slowly, you can play it quickly!*DE: Kleiner, feiner Modeschmuck mit einer winzigen, in goldenem Rahmen eingefassten Biene auf weißem, leicht schimmernden Hintergrund in Perlmutt-Optik, hergestellt mit viel Liebe und per Hand aus Modelliermasse.Die Biene ist an einem goldenen Ring und einem goldenen Ohrringhaken befestigt und sind federleicht.(Kann auch auf Anfrage zum Klip-Ohrring angepasst werden.)*EN: The circle-shaped background of this little trinket was made by hand with lots of love out of polymer clay, in a slight shimmery, pearly-white color. I've been watching and listening a lot to those two very likeable guys while cutting, rolling and baking clay those past months. It's been years since I had last listened to classical music and Twoset got me into it once more, thankfully.  The model on the photo wearing the earrings is called Lisa, she's got an Instagram account called "lisamarieview." Danke, Lisa!

name: Necklace Triskele Triple Spiral Wood Burned
description: Unique men's or ladies wooden necklace.Triple spiral(Druidism): Derived from the Greek word "Triskeles" meaning "three legs", the Triskele or Triple Spiral is a complex ancient Celtic symbol. Often referred to by many as a Triskelion, its earliest creation dates back to the Neolithic era, as it can be seen at the entrance of Newgrange, Ireland. The Triskele gained popularity in its use within the Celtic culture from 500BC onwards. This archaic symbol is one of the most convoluted to decipher as symbolists believe it is reflective of many areas of culture from the time.1)The motion of action, cycles, progress, revolution and competition.2)Life-death-rebirth, spirit-mind-body, mother-father-child, past-present-future, power-intellect-love and creation-preservation-destructionIt’s thought that through the combination of these two areas we gain one meaning of the Celtic triskele. It is believed to represent a tale of forward motion to reach understanding. However, this is thought not to be the only meaning, as it is also believed to represent three Celtic worlds; the spiritual world, the present world and the celestial world. Like the ancient Trinity knot, the number 3 holds a special symbolism within the triskele.Material:Wood: Beech WoodCord:  Cotton Waxed CordVarnish: Odorless Wood Varnish for children's toysApproximate Dimensions:Size:  35mm x 35mm x ~5mmCord Size: AdjustablePlease note that this item is handmade, so there may be small differences comparing with the photo.If you have any inquiries, please don’t hesitate to contact me.
